INSERT INTO LY_QRY_SQL
SELECT
  :QUERY_ID QUERY_ID,
  'generic' QUERY_DBTYPE,
  'GET' QUERY_CRUD,
  :QUERY_POOL,
  QUERY_SQLQUERY,
  QUERY_ORDERBY QUERY_ORDERBY,
  :AUDIT_USER AUDIT_USER,
  :AUDIT_DATE AUDIT_DATE
FROM
(
SELECT 
  LKP_ID,
  LKP_ORDERBY QUERY_ORDERBY,
  'SELECT 
  ' || STRING_AGG(
       DISTINCT LKP_COLUMNS,
        ',
  '
       ORDER BY LKP_COLUMNS 
    ) || ' 
FROM 
  ' || (SELECT TBL_DB_NAME FROM LY_TABLES WHERE TBL_ID = :LKP_TBL_ID)
    AS QUERY_SQLQUERY
FROM
(
SELECT 
  LY_LOOKUP.LKP_ID,
  COALESCE(LKP_DD_GROUP||',', '') || LKP_DD_ID AS LKP_ORDERBY,
  unnest(array_remove(array[LKP_DD_ID, LKP_DD_LABEL, LKP_DD_GROUP, DD_ID], null)) AS LKP_COLUMNS
FROM
  LY_LOOKUP
LEFT JOIN
  LY_LKP_PARAMS
  ON LY_LKP_PARAMS.LKP_ID = LY_LOOKUP.LKP_ID
)
GROUP BY LKP_ID, LKP_ORDERBY
)
WHERE LKP_ID = :LKP_ID

SELECT
  TBL_QUERY_ID QUERY_ID,
  'generic' QUERY_DBTYPE,
  'POST' QUERY_CRUD,
  :QUERY_POOL,
  QUERY_SQLQUERY,
  null QUERY_ORDERBY,

  :AUDIT_DATE
FROM
(
SELECT
    TBL_QUERY_ID,
    'INSERT INTO
    ' || TBL_DB_NAME || '
(
    ' || STRING_AGG(
       COL_TARGET,
        ',
    '
       ORDER BY COL_SEQ
    ) || '
)
VALUES (
    ' || STRING_AGG(
       ':'||COL_TARGET,
        ',
    '
       ORDER BY COL_SEQ
    )|| '
)' 
AS QUERY_SQLQUERY
FROM
  LY_TBL_COL
INNER JOIN
  LY_TABLES ON LY_TABLES.TBL_ID = LY_TBL_COL.TBL_ID
WHERE LY_TABLES.TBL_ID = :TBL_ID
GROUP BY TBL_QUERY_ID, TBL_DB_NAME
)

FROM

SELECT

    'SELECT

       COL_TARGET,

    ) || '

INSERT INTO LY_QRY_SQL
SELECT
  TBL_QUERY_ID QUERY_ID,
  'generic' QUERY_DBTYPE,
  'PUT' QUERY_CRUD,
  :QUERY_POOL,
  QUERY_SQLQUERY,
  null QUERY_ORDERBY,
  :AUDIT_USER,
  :AUDIT_DATE
FROM
(
SELECT
    TBL_QUERY_ID,
    'UPDATE
    ' || TBL_DB_NAME || '
SET
    ' || STRING_AGG(
       CASE WHEN COL_KEY = 'N' THEN COL_TARGET||' = :'||COL_TARGET ELSE NULL END,
        ',
    '
       ORDER BY COL_SEQ
    ) || '
WHERE
    ' || STRING_AGG(
       CASE WHEN COL_KEY = 'Y' THEN COL_TARGET||' = :'||COL_TARGET ELSE NULL END,
        '
    AND '
       ORDER BY COL_SEQ
    ) 
AS QUERY_SQLQUERY
FROM
  LY_TBL_COL
INNER JOIN
  LY_TABLES ON LY_TABLES.TBL_ID = LY_TBL_COL.TBL_ID
WHERE LY_TABLES.TBL_ID = :TBL_ID
GROUP BY TBL_QUERY_ID, TBL_DB_NAME
)

SELECT  DISTINCT 
  TBL_ID,
  COL_DD_ID DD_ID, 
  CASE 
        WHEN COL_DD_ID LIKE '%AUDIT_DATE' THEN 'Date (Audit)'
        WHEN COL_DD_ID LIKE '%AUDIT_USER' THEN 'User (Audit)'
        WHEN COL_DD_ID LIKE '%LABEL' THEN 'Description'
        END DD_LABEL,
  CASE 
        WHEN data_type like 'timestamp%' THEN  'date' 
        WHEN data_type ='integer' THEN  'number' 
        WHEN data_type ='character varying' THEN  'text' 
        WHEN data_type ='varchar' THEN  'text' 
        WHEN data_type ='text' THEN  'textarea' 
        END DD_TYPE,
    CASE 
        WHEN COL_DD_ID LIKE '%AUDIT_DATE' THEN 'SYSDATE'
        WHEN COL_DD_ID LIKE '%AUDIT_USER' THEN 'LOGIN'
        END  DD_RULES,
  null DD_RULES_VALUES,
  null DD_DEFAULT,
  'admin' DD_AUDIT_USER,
  CURRENT_DATE DD_AUDIT_DATE ,
  'Y' ADD_ROW
FROM
  LY_TBL_COL
LEFT JOIN
  information_schema.columns
  ON UPPER(column_name) = COL_TARGET
WHERE 
COL_DD_ID NOT IN (SELECT DD_ID FROM LY_DICTIONARY)

INSERT INTO LY_QRY_SQL
SELECT
  SEQ_QUERY_ID QUERY_ID,
  'generic' QUERY_DBTYPE,
  'GET' QUERY_CRUD,
  :QUERY_POOL,
  QUERY_SQLQUERY,
  NULL QUERY_ORDERBY,
  :AUDIT_USER AUDIT_USER,
  :AUDIT_DATE AUDIT_DATE
FROM
(
SELECT 
  SEQ_ID,
  SEQ_QUERY_ID,
  'SELECT   
  MAX(' || SEQ_DD_ID || ') AS SEQ_VALUE' || COALESCE(',
  '||SEQ_GROUPBY, '') || ' 
FROM 
  ' || (SELECT TBL_DB_NAME FROM LY_TABLES WHERE TBL_ID = :SEQ_TBL_ID) 
  ||  COALESCE('
GROUP BY 
  '|| SEQ_GROUPBY, '') AS QUERY_SQLQUERY
FROM
(
SELECT 
  LY_SEQUENCE.SEQ_ID,
  LY_SEQUENCE.SEQ_QUERY_ID,
  LY_SEQUENCE.SEQ_DD_ID,
  STRING_AGG(    
  DISTINCT DD_ID,
        ',
  '
       ORDER BY DD_ID 
    ) AS SEQ_GROUPBY
FROM
  LY_SEQUENCE
LEFT JOIN
  LY_SEQ_PARAMS
  ON LY_SEQ_PARAMS.SEQ_ID = LY_SEQUENCE.SEQ_ID
GROUP BY LY_SEQUENCE.SEQ_ID, LY_SEQUENCE.SEQ_QUERY_ID, LY_SEQUENCE.SEQ_DD_ID
)
GROUP BY SEQ_ID, SEQ_QUERY_ID, SEQ_DD_ID, SEQ_GROUPBY
)
WHERE SEQ_ID = :SEQ_ID

FROM
(
  SELECT
    'BOOLEAN' DD_RULES,

    'Enable (Y)' LKP_LABEL
  UNION ALL
  SELECT
    'BOOLEAN' DD_RULES,
    '01' DD_RULES_VALUES,
    'Enable (01)' LKP_LABEL
  UNION ALL
   SELECT * FROM (
   SELECT
    'ENUM' COL_RULES,
    CAST(ENUM_ID AS VARCHAR) DD_RULES_VALUES,
    ENUM_LABEL LKP_LABEL
  FROM
    LY_ENUM
  ORDER BY
    ENUM_ID
    )
  UNION ALL
  SELECT DD_RULES,  CAST(DD_RULES_VALUES AS VARCHAR) DD_RULES_VALUES, LKP_LABEL FROM (
   SELECT
    'LOOKUP' DD_RULES,
    LKP_ID DD_RULES_VALUES,
    LKP_DESCRIPTION LKP_LABEL
   FROM
    LY_LOOKUP  
   ORDER BY LKP_ID
  )  
  UNION ALL
   SELECT
    'NN' DD_RULES,
    NN_ID DD_RULES_VALUES,
    'Next Number - '||NN_ID LKP_LABEL
  FROM
    LY_NEXTNUM 
  UNION ALL
  SELECT * FROM (
   SELECT
    'SEQUENCE' DD_RULES,
    CAST(SEQ_ID AS VARCHAR) DD_RULES_VALUES,
    SEQ_LABEL LKP_LABEL
   FROM
    LY_SEQUENCE  
   ORDER BY SEQ_ID
   )
  UNION ALL
  SELECT
    'DEFAULT' DD_RULES,
    DD_ID DD_RULES_VALUES,
    DD_LABEL LKP_LABEL
  FROM
    LY_DICTIONARY
 )

SELECT
  TRIM(UPPER(SUBSTR(COLUMN_NAME, 3))) AS DD_ID,
  TRIM(FRDSCR) DD_LABEL,
  CASE 
    WHEN TRIM(FROWTP)='9' THEN 'number'
    WHEN TRIM(FROWTP)='11' THEN 'number'
    WHEN TRIM(FROWTP)='2' THEN 'text'
    WHEN TRIM(FROWTP)='1' THEN 'text'
    ELSE 'text'
  END DD_TYPE,
  CASE 
    WHEN TRIM(FROWER) = 'UDC' THEN CAST('LOOKUP' AS VARCHAR(20))
    ELSE NULL
  END DD_RULES,
  CASE 
    WHEN TRIM(FROWER) = 'UDC' THEN CAST('1' AS VARCHAR(50))
    ELSE NULL
  END DD_RULES_VALUES,
  TRIM(FRDVAL) AS DD_DEFAULT,
  :DD_AUDIT_USER AS DD_AUDIT_USER,
  :DD_AUDIT_DATE AS DD_AUDIT_DATE
FROM
  ALL_TAB_COLUMNS
INNER JOIN 
  #:DD_SCHEMA#.F9200 ON TRIM(F9200.FRDTAI) = TRIM(UPPER(SUBSTR(COLUMN_NAME, 3)))
INNER JOIN 
  #:DD_SCHEMA#.F9202 
  ON F9202.FRDTAI = F9200.FRDTAI AND TRIM(F9202.FRSYR) is NULL
INNER JOIN 
  #:DD_SCHEMA#.F9210 
  ON F9210.FRDTAI = F9200.FRDTAI    
WHERE
  UPPER(TABLE_NAME) = UPPER(:TBL_DB_NAME)
  AND UPPER(OWNER) = UPPER(:TBL_SCHEMA)
ORDER BY
  COLUMN_ID

SELECT
  TRIM(UPPER(SUBSTR(COLUMN_NAME, 3))) AS DD_ID,
  t.FLT_ID,
  'VALUE' AS FLT_TYPE,
  NULL AS FLT_SOURCE,
  CASE t.FLT_ID
    WHEN 1 THEN 'SY'   -- When FLT_ID = 1, use TARGET_SY (FROER1)
    WHEN 2 THEN 'RT'   -- When FLT_ID = 2, use TARGET_RT (FROER2)
  END AS FLT_TARGET,
  CASE t.FLT_ID
    WHEN 1 THEN TRIM(FROER1)   -- When FLT_ID = 1, use TARGET_SY (FROER1)
    WHEN 2 THEN TRIM(FROER2)   -- When FLT_ID = 2, use TARGET_RT (FROER2)
  END AS FLT_VALUE,
  :DD_AUDIT_USER,
  :DD_AUDIT_DATE
FROM
  ALL_TAB_COLUMNS
INNER JOIN 
  #:DD_SCHEMA#.F9200 ON TRIM(F9200.FRDTAI) = TRIM(UPPER(SUBSTR(COLUMN_NAME, 3)))
INNER JOIN 
  #:DD_SCHEMA#.F9210 
  ON F9210.FRDTAI = F9200.FRDTAI
CROSS JOIN
  (SELECT 1 AS FLT_ID FROM DUAL
   UNION ALL
   SELECT 2 AS FLT_ID FROM DUAL) t
WHERE
  UPPER(TABLE_NAME) = UPPER(:TBL_DB_NAME)
  AND UPPER(OWNER) = UPPER(:TBL_SCHEMA)
  AND TRIM(FROWER) = 'UDC'
ORDER BY
  COLUMN_ID, FLT_ID

SELECT
    LY_TABLES.TBL_ID,
    TBL_DB_NAME,
    TBL_LABEL,
    TBL_QUERY_ID,
    QUERY_POOL,
    TBL_EDITABLE,
    TBL_UPLOADABLE,
    TBL_AUDIT,
    TBL_BURST,
    TBL_WORKBOOK,
    TBL_SHEET,
    TBL_CTX_ID,
    TBL_TREE_ID,
    TBL_FRM_ID,
    COALESCE(FRM_LABEL,TBL_LABEL) FRM_LABEL,
    STRING_AGG(
       COALESCE(COL_TARGET, COL_DD_ID),
        ';'
       ORDER BY COL_SEQ 
    ) AS TBL_KEY,
    TBL_AUTO_LOAD
FROM
    LY_TABLES
INNER JOIN
  (SELECT QUERY_ID, QUERY_POOL FROM LY_QRY_SQL WHERE QUERY_CRUD = 'GET' GROUP BY QUERY_ID,QUERY_POOL) AS LY_QRY_SQL
        ON QUERY_ID = TBL_QUERY_ID 
LEFT JOIN LY_TBL_COL ON LY_TBL_COL.TBL_ID = LY_TABLES.TBL_ID AND COL_KEY='Y'
LEFT JOIN LY_DLG_FRM ON LY_DLG_FRM.FRM_ID = TBL_FRM_ID
GROUP BY
    LY_TABLES.TBL_ID,
    TBL_LABEL,
    TBL_QUERY_ID,
    QUERY_POOL,
    TBL_EDITABLE,
    TBL_UPLOADABLE,
    TBL_AUDIT,
    TBL_BURST,
    TBL_WORKBOOK,
    TBL_SHEET,
    TBL_CTX_ID,
    TBL_TREE_ID,
    TBL_FRM_ID,

    LY_LINKS

    AUT_RUN,
     STRING_AGG(
        CASE WHEN (FLT_TYPE='DD' AND FLT_SOURCE IS NOT NULL) THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(FLT_TARGET, FLT_SOURCE)||'='||FLT_SOURCE END,
        ';'
        ORDER BY FLT_ID
    ) AS DYNAMIC_PARAMS,
    STRING_AGG(
       CASE WHEN (FLT_TYPE='VALUE' AND FLT_VALUE IS NOT NULL) THEN FLT_TARGET||'='||FLT_VALUE ELSE NULL END,
        ';'
        ORDER BY FLT_ID
    ) AS FIXED_PARAMS  
FROM (
SELECT
    USR_ID,
    MENU_COMPONENT,
    MENU_COMPONENT_ID,
    COALESCE(LNG_LABEL, MENU_LABEL) MENU_LABEL,
    LY_MENUS.MENU_SEQ_UKID KEY_ATTRIBUTES,
    MENU_PARENT_ID,
    LY_MENUS.MENU_CHILD_ID,
    MENU_LEVEL,
    AUT_RUN    
FROM
    LY_MENUS
INNER JOIN (
WITH RECURSIVE USR_MENUS AS (
   SELECT 
     USR.USR_ID USR_ID,ROL_ID,MENU_CHILD_ID, COALESCE(AUT_RUN, USR_ADMIN) RUN
   FROM 
     LY_MENUS 
   INNER JOIN (
     SELECT 
        LY_USERS.USR_ID,USR_ADMIN
     FROM
        LY_USERS
     ) USR ON 1 = 1
   LEFT JOIN (
     SELECT 
        USR_ID,LY_ROL_AUTH.ROL_ID,AUT_MENU_SEQ_UKID, AUT_RUN 
     FROM 
        LY_USR_ROLES 
     LEFT JOIN
        LY_ROL_AUTH ON LY_ROL_AUTH.ROL_ID = LY_USR_ROLES.ROL_ID   
     ) AUTH ON AUTH.AUT_MENU_SEQ_UKID = LY_MENUS.MENU_SEQ_UKID AND AUTH.USR_ID = USR.USR_ID
   WHERE 
     MENU_LEVEL = 1
   UNION ALL
   SELECT 
    CHILD_MENUS.USR_ID, CHILD_MENUS.ROL_ID, PARENT_MENUS.MENU_CHILD_ID, COALESCE(AUT_RUN, RUN) RUN
   FROM 
     LY_MENUS AS PARENT_MENUS
   INNER JOIN 
     USR_MENUS CHILD_MENUS ON CHILD_MENUS.MENU_CHILD_ID = PARENT_MENUS.MENU_PARENT_ID  
   LEFT JOIN (
     SELECT 
        USR_ID,LY_ROL_AUTH.ROL_ID, AUT_MENU_SEQ_UKID, AUT_RUN 
     FROM 
        LY_USR_ROLES 
     LEFT JOIN
        LY_ROL_AUTH ON LY_ROL_AUTH.ROL_ID = LY_USR_ROLES.ROL_ID   
     ) AUTH ON AUTH.AUT_MENU_SEQ_UKID = PARENT_MENUS.MENU_SEQ_UKID AND AUTH.USR_ID = CHILD_MENUS.USR_ID AND AUTH.ROL_ID = CHILD_MENUS.ROL_ID

)
SELECT 
  USR_ID, MENU_CHILD_ID, MAX(RUN) AUT_RUN
FROM 
  USR_MENUS 
GROUP BY
  USR_ID, MENU_CHILD_ID
) AUTH ON LY_MENUS.MENU_SEQ_UKID = AUTH.MENU_CHILD_ID
LEFT JOIN LY_MENUS_L
    ON LY_MENUS_L.LNG_ID = :LNG_ID AND LNG_SEQ_UKID = MENU_SEQ_UKID
) MENUS
LEFT JOIN
  LY_MENUS_FILTERS FLT
  ON FLT.MENU_SEQ_UKID = MENUS.KEY_ATTRIBUTES 
 GROUP BY
    LNG_ID,
    USR_ID,
    MENU_COMPONENT,
    MENU_COMPONENT_ID,
    MENU_LABEL,
    KEY_ATTRIBUTES,
    MENU_PARENT_ID,

    AUT_RUN

                    THEN FLT_TARGET || '=' || FLT_VALUE 
                ELSE NULL 
            END, 
            ';'
            ORDER BY FLT_ID
        ) AS DD_FIXED_PARAMS
    FROM LY_DICTIONARY
    LEFT JOIN LY_DICTIONARY_FILTERS FLT ON FLT.DD_ID = LY_DICTIONARY.DD_ID
    GROUP BY 
        LY_DICTIONARY.DD_ID,

),
Dialog_CTE AS (
    SELECT 
        :LNG_ID AS LNG_ID,
        LY_DLG_FRM.FRM_ID,
        LY_DLG_TAB.TAB_ID,
        CONCAT(LY_DLG_FRM.FRM_ID, '-tab-id-', COALESCE(TAB_SEQ, 1)) AS TAB_SEQ,
        COL_ID,
        COL_SEQ,
        COL_COLSPAN,
        COL_COMPONENT,
        COL_COMPONENT_ID,
        COL_DD_ID,
        COALESCE(DD.DD_LABEL, COALESCE(COL_LABEL, CAST(COL_COMPONENT_ID AS VARCHAR))) AS COL_LABEL,
        COL_TARGET,
        COALESCE(DD.DD_TYPE, COALESCE(COL_TYPE, 'text')) AS COL_TYPE,
        COALESCE(COL_RULES, DD.DD_RULES) AS COL_RULES,
        COALESCE(COL_RULES_VALUES, DD.DD_RULES_VALUES) AS COL_RULES_VALUES,
        COALESCE(COL_DEFAULT, DD.DD_DEFAULT) AS COL_DEFAULT,
        COL_VISIBLE,
        COL_DISABLED,
        COL_REQUIRED,
        COL_KEY,
        COL_CDN_ID,
        DD_FIXED_PARAMS
    FROM LY_DLG_FRM
    INNER JOIN LY_DLG_COL ON LY_DLG_COL.FRM_ID = LY_DLG_FRM.FRM_ID 
    LEFT JOIN LY_DLG_TAB ON LY_DLG_TAB.FRM_ID = LY_DLG_FRM.FRM_ID AND LY_DLG_TAB.TAB_ID = LY_DLG_COL.TAB_ID
    LEFT JOIN Dictionary_CTE DD ON DD.DD_ID = COL_DD_ID AND DD.DD_LANGUAGE = :LNG_ID
),
FilteredDialog_CTE AS (
    SELECT 
        DLG.LNG_ID,
        DLG.FRM_ID,
        DLG.TAB_ID,
        DLG.TAB_SEQ,
        DLG.COL_ID,
        COL_SEQ,
        COL_COLSPAN,
        COL_COMPONENT,
        COL_COMPONENT_ID,
        COL_DD_ID,
        COL_LABEL,
        COL_TARGET,
        COL_TYPE,
        COL_RULES,
        COL_RULES_VALUES,
        COL_DEFAULT,
        COL_VISIBLE,
        COL_DISABLED,
        COL_REQUIRED,
        COL_KEY,
        COL_CDN_ID,
        DD_FIXED_PARAMS,
        STRING_AGG(
            CASE 
                WHEN FLT_TYPE = 'DD' AND FLT_SOURCE IS NOT NULL 
                    THEN COALESCE(FLT_TARGET, FLT_SOURCE) || '=' || FLT_SOURCE 
                ELSE NULL 
            END, 
            ';'
            ORDER BY FLT_ID
        ) AS DYNAMIC_PARAMS,
        STRING_AGG(
            CASE 
                WHEN FLT_TYPE = 'VALUE' AND FLT_VALUE IS NOT NULL 
                    THEN FLT_TARGET || '=' || FLT_VALUE 
                ELSE NULL 
            END, 
            ';'
            ORDER BY FLT_ID
        ) AS FIXED_PARAMS,
        STRING_AGG(
            CASE 
                WHEN FLT_TYPE = 'POOL' 
                    THEN COALESCE(FLT_SOURCE, FLT_VALUE) 
                ELSE NULL 
            END, 
            ';'
            ORDER BY FLT_ID
        ) AS POOL_PARAMS,
        STRING_AGG(
            CASE 
                WHEN FLT_TYPE = 'OUT' AND FLT_SOURCE IS NOT NULL 
                    THEN COALESCE(FLT_TARGET, FLT_SOURCE) || '=' || FLT_SOURCE 
                ELSE NULL 
            END, 
            ';'
            ORDER BY FLT_ID
        ) AS OUTPUT_PARAMS
    FROM Dialog_CTE DLG
    LEFT JOIN LY_DLG_FILTERS FLT ON FLT.FRM_ID = DLG.FRM_ID AND FLT.COL_ID = DLG.COL_ID
    GROUP BY
        DLG.LNG_ID,
        DLG.FRM_ID,
        DLG.TAB_ID,
        DLG.TAB_SEQ,
        DLG.COL_ID,
        COL_SEQ,
        COL_COLSPAN,
        COL_COMPONENT,
        COL_COMPONENT_ID,
        COL_DD_ID,
        COL_LABEL,
        COL_TARGET,
        COL_TYPE,
        COL_RULES,
        COL_RULES_VALUES,
        COL_DEFAULT,
        COL_VISIBLE,
        COL_DISABLED,
        COL_REQUIRED,
        COL_KEY,
        COL_CDN_ID,
        DD_FIXED_PARAMS
)

  CDN_GROUP,
  CDN_LABEL,
  CDN_LOGICAL
FROM
  LY_CDN_GRP

WITH Dictionary_CTE AS (
    SELECT
        :LNG_ID AS DD_LANGUAGE,
        DD.DD_ID,
        COALESCE(LNG_LABEL, DD_LABEL) AS DD_LABEL,
        DD_TYPE,
        DD_RULES,
        DD_RULES_VALUES,
        DD_DEFAULT,
        DD_AUDIT_USER,
        DD_AUDIT_DATE,
        DD_FIXED_PARAMS
    FROM
    (
    SELECT
        LY_DICTIONARY.DD_ID, 
        DD_LABEL,
        DD_TYPE,
        DD_RULES,
        DD_RULES_VALUES,
        DD_DEFAULT,
        DD_AUDIT_USER,
        DD_AUDIT_DATE,   
        STRING_AGG(
            CASE 
                WHEN FLT_TYPE = 'VALUE' AND FLT_VALUE IS NOT NULL 
                    THEN FLT_TARGET || '=' || FLT_VALUE 
                ELSE NULL 
            END, 
            ';'
            ORDER BY FLT_ID
        ) AS DD_FIXED_PARAMS
    FROM LY_DICTIONARY
    LEFT JOIN LY_DICTIONARY_FILTERS FLT ON FLT.DD_ID = LY_DICTIONARY.DD_ID
    GROUP BY 
        LY_DICTIONARY.DD_ID,
        DD_LABEL,
        DD_TYPE,
        DD_RULES,
        DD_RULES_VALUES,
        DD_DEFAULT,
        DD_AUDIT_USER,
        DD_AUDIT_DATE
    ) DD
    LEFT JOIN LY_DICTIONARY_L
        ON LY_DICTIONARY_L.LNG_ID = :LNG_ID AND LY_DICTIONARY_L.DD_ID = DD.DD_ID
),
Table_CTE AS (
    SELECT 
        :LNG_ID AS LNG_ID,
        LY_TABLES.TBL_ID,
        COL_ID,
        COL_SEQ,
        COL_DD_ID,
        COALESCE(DD_LABEL, COALESCE(COL_LABEL, COL_DD_ID)) COL_LABEL,
        COL_TARGET,
        COALESCE(DD_TYPE, COALESCE(COL_TYPE, 'text')) COL_TYPE,
        COALESCE(COL_RULES, DD_RULES) COL_RULES,
        COALESCE(COL_RULES_VALUES, DD_RULES_VALUES) COL_RULES_VALUES,
        COALESCE(COL_DEFAULT, DD_DEFAULT) COL_DEFAULT,
        COL_VISIBLE,
        COL_DISABLED,
        COL_REQUIRED,
        COL_KEY,
        COL_FILTER,
        DD_FIXED_PARAMS,
        COL_CDN_ID
    FROM LY_TABLES
    INNER JOIN LY_TBL_COL ON LY_TBL_COL.TBL_ID = LY_TABLES.TBL_ID 
    LEFT JOIN Dictionary_CTE DD ON DD.DD_ID = COL_DD_ID AND DD.DD_LANGUAGE = :LNG_ID
),
FilteredTable_CTE AS (
    SELECT 
        TBL.LNG_ID,
        TBL.TBL_ID,
        TBL.COL_ID,
        COL_SEQ,
        COL_DD_ID,
        COL_LABEL,
        COL_TARGET,
        COL_TYPE,
        COL_RULES,
        COL_RULES_VALUES,
        COL_DEFAULT,
        COL_VISIBLE,
        COL_DISABLED,
        COL_REQUIRED,
        COL_KEY,
        COL_FILTER,
        DD_FIXED_PARAMS,
        COL_CDN_ID,
        STRING_AGG(
            CASE 
                WHEN FLT_TYPE = 'DD' AND FLT_SOURCE IS NOT NULL 
                    THEN COALESCE(FLT_TARGET, FLT_SOURCE) || '=' || FLT_SOURCE 
                ELSE NULL 
            END, 
            ';'
            ORDER BY FLT_ID
        ) AS DYNAMIC_PARAMS,
        STRING_AGG(
            CASE 
                WHEN FLT_TYPE = 'VALUE' AND FLT_VALUE IS NOT NULL 
                    THEN FLT_TARGET || '=' || FLT_VALUE 
                ELSE NULL 
            END, 
            ';'
            ORDER BY FLT_ID
        ) AS FIXED_PARAMS,
        STRING_AGG(
            CASE 
                WHEN FLT_TYPE = 'POOL' 
                    THEN COALESCE(FLT_SOURCE, FLT_VALUE) 
                ELSE NULL 
            END, 
            ';'
            ORDER BY FLT_ID
        ) AS POOL_PARAMS,
        STRING_AGG(
            CASE 
                WHEN FLT_TYPE = 'OUT' AND FLT_SOURCE IS NOT NULL 
                    THEN COALESCE(FLT_TARGET, FLT_SOURCE) || '=' || FLT_SOURCE 
                ELSE NULL 
            END, 
            ';'
            ORDER BY FLT_ID
        ) AS OUTPUT_PARAMS
    FROM Table_CTE TBL
    LEFT JOIN LY_TBL_FILTERS FLT ON FLT.TBL_ID = TBL.TBL_ID AND FLT.COL_ID = TBL.COL_ID
    GROUP BY
        TBL.LNG_ID,
        TBL.TBL_ID,
        TBL.COL_ID,
        COL_SEQ,
        COL_DD_ID,
        COL_LABEL,
        COL_TARGET,
        COL_TYPE,
        COL_RULES,
        COL_RULES_VALUES,
        COL_DEFAULT,
        COL_VISIBLE,
        COL_DISABLED,
        COL_REQUIRED,
        COL_KEY,
        COL_FILTER,
        DD_FIXED_PARAMS,
        COL_CDN_ID
)
SELECT 
    TBL_COL.LNG_ID,
    TBL_COL.TBL_ID,
    TBL_COL.COL_ID,
    TBL_COL.COL_SEQ,
    TBL_COL.COL_DD_ID,
    TBL_COL.COL_LABEL,
    TBL_COL.COL_TARGET,
    TBL_COL.COL_TYPE,
    TBL_COL.COL_RULES,
    TBL_COL.COL_RULES_VALUES,
    TBL_COL.COL_DEFAULT,
    TBL_COL.COL_VISIBLE,
    TBL_COL.COL_DISABLED,
    TBL_COL.COL_REQUIRED,
    TBL_COL.COL_KEY,
    TBL_COL.COL_FILTER,
    TBL_COL.DYNAMIC_PARAMS,
    COALESCE(TBL_COL.FIXED_PARAMS, DD_FIXED_PARAMS) FIXED_PARAMS,
    TBL_COL.POOL_PARAMS,
    TBL_COL.OUTPUT_PARAMS,
    TBL_COL.COL_CDN_ID,
    STRING_AGG(
        CASE 
            WHEN CDN_TYPE = 'DD' AND CDN_SOURCE IS NOT NULL 
                THEN CDN_TARGET || '=' || CDN_SOURCE 
            ELSE NULL 
        END, 
        ';'
    ) AS CDN_DYNAMIC_PARAMS,
    STRING_AGG(
        CASE 
            WHEN CDN_TYPE = 'VALUE' AND CDN_VALUE IS NOT NULL 
                THEN CDN_TARGET || '=' || CDN_VALUE 
            ELSE NULL 
        END, 
        ';'
    ) AS CDN_FIXED_PARAMS
FROM FilteredTable_CTE TBL_COL
LEFT JOIN LY_TBL_COL_CDN CDN ON CDN.TBL_ID = TBL_COL.TBL_ID AND CDN.COL_ID = TBL_COL.COL_ID
GROUP BY
    TBL_COL.LNG_ID,
    TBL_COL.TBL_ID,
    TBL_COL.COL_ID,
    TBL_COL.COL_SEQ,
    TBL_COL.COL_DD_ID,
    TBL_COL.COL_LABEL,
    TBL_COL.COL_TARGET,
    TBL_COL.COL_TYPE,
    TBL_COL.COL_RULES,
    TBL_COL.COL_RULES_VALUES,
    TBL_COL.COL_DEFAULT,
    TBL_COL.COL_VISIBLE,
    TBL_COL.COL_DISABLED,
    TBL_COL.COL_REQUIRED,
    TBL_COL.COL_KEY,
    TBL_COL.COL_FILTER,
    TBL_COL.DYNAMIC_PARAMS,
    COALESCE(TBL_COL.FIXED_PARAMS, DD_FIXED_PARAMS),
    TBL_COL.POOL_PARAMS,
    TBL_COL.OUTPUT_PARAMS,
    TBL_COL.COL_CDN_ID
